Interface ICalendarRendering

CalendarRenderer
public interface ICalendarRendering

The contract that must be offered by any renderer that wishes to render SimpleCalendar widgets.

Method Detail

getSelection

int getSelection(SimpleCalendar calendar,
                 int x,
                 int y)
Returns the day of month in range [0..daysInMonth-1], or PREVIOUS_MONTH_COMMAND to go to the previous month, or NEXT_MONTH_COMMAND to go to the next month, or INVALID otherwise.

Parameters:
calendar - the SimpleCalendar widget
x - the x position, relative to the widget bounds, of the pointer
y - the y position, relative to the widget bounds, of the pointer
Returns:
the date selection index or a command or INVALID
